headline: MetLife Upgraded To Buy As Financials And Insurance Show Further Upside Potential
summary: MetLife has a 10-year track record of proven dividend growth, something it has potential to continue. Read why I upgrade MET stock from hold to buy.

headline: MetLife’s Malaysia Center of Excellence Celebrates 5th Anniversary
summary: KUALA LUMPUR, Malaysia, November 26, 2024--Global insurer MetLife celebrated the 5th anniversary of its Malaysia Center of Excellence (COE) on November 22, a key milestone reflecting growth in its hiring, operations, and community activities.
